{"tid":665833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中客穿「南海九段線」入境越南 被當地警方要求脫衣","createTime":"2018-05-15T10:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T01:27:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e14bb2812807203e1aaeb11f27faa217a019373d","tid":665833,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpcEhXaH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpcEhXaH.jpg&h=55590143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-14 23:58<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南海主權議題敏感，一批中國遊客在13日晚間入境越南時，身穿中國外加「南海九段線」領土的T恤，當場被機場警察攔下要求更衣，目前事件已交由當局相關單位處理。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，一群中國遊客日前搭乘編號QJ 8889班機，從西安出發前往越南芽莊市（Th&agrave;nh phố Nha Trang），預計停留5天。<br />\n<br />\n但當他們到達越南機場，辦理入境手續時，機場警察發現他們全都身穿南海九段線的衣服，與旅行社溝通後，要求他們全數更換上衣，並將南海九段線T恤交由越南警方。<br />\n<br />\n金蘭國際機場正與慶和省警方配合處理，事件已上報省政府，將與相關單位配合調閱機場監視器影片，釐清事件。<br />\n<br />\n中方宣稱南海自古以來都屬於中國領土，擁有九段線內海域的主權，但海牙的常設仲裁法院於2016年裁決中國「九段線」在國際法之下沒有效力，沒有法律根據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2425919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2425919&d=fPrERKXOLSGnjnJt4dppowdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0d35cc0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2425919&h=a0187c45\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2425919</a>"},{"pid":"8ed0a092df05e0a09de79cbae5eac20a74e6dd84","tid":665833,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"支那人&hellip;<br />\n越南咁就算？"},{"pid":"232363585b5774454d667b343f123876d3369b1a","tid":665833,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"on9到震"},{"pid":"365db479833c1013d3038b50af4bc9578171af4c","tid":665833,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"血染的風采"},{"pid":"d16e77a094762978d39dfce152c495be8bf84997","tid":665833,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"咁都唔譴返有無攪錯"}]}